node.text:
@being1ton 
Welcome to the Ultimate Yun Tun Feast! Or Wanton Feast! However you want to put it, @being1ton offers one of the best Wantons ontop of their already delicious wanton mee! From the steam one, fried ones to the dumplings, which are all perfectly executed! Bear in mind, even though I got these delivered, the fried ones are still crispy and crunchy!
🔻
Something that I found extraordinarily was their dumpling soup! It was so appetizing and full of Umami! This is a ‘must order’ when you are ordering from @being1ton !
📱whatsapp 𝟔𝟓𝟗𝟎𝟒𝟔𝟕𝟏𝟕𝟔 to order!
🚙Island wide delivery available!
🏢
